Popular socialite, Obi Cubana and his elder brother, Ike Iyiegbu have felicitated with veteran actor, Nkem Owoh aka Osuofia on the occasion of his birthday. The Cubana brothers via posts on their insta stories celebrated with the movie icon on his 64th birthday.   BREAKING: NFF names Amuneke new Super Eagles coach     Benin Republic extends Sunday Igboho’s detention by ‘six…     Supreme Court fixes judgment for May 6 in Rivers, Imo…   Owoh, who has entertained Nigerians for decades seeing the niche he’s been able to carve for himself as a foremost comic act, was described as a legend by the Cubana brothers. The billionaire nightlife boss in his post shared his photo of Nkem Owoh with the caption: “Happy birthday legend.” Ike Cubana, aslo sharing a photo of Osuofio wrote: “Happy birthday, ezigbo mmadu (good man)… a legend.”